          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1685114275058-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>white long grain rice </strong>to a pot with a lid with the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam – this is your <strong>coconut rice</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>tomatoes </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
